Description: Dallah Healthcare Co (known as: Dallah Healthcare) is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Tadawul” (TDWL) since December 2012. Dallah Health operates within the Health Care Equipment and Services sector focusing on Health Care Facilities. It has Companies operating across Jordan and Saudi Arabia. Dallah Healthcare is based in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia and was established in September 1994.
